          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A highly pure (>99.9%) thin natural boron target",
                "deposited on a 6 mu-m Al substrate (Goodfellows",
                "microfoil) was used for the experiments. The actual",
                "target thickness was found to be much lower",
                " (157 x 10**15 at/cm2 +- 10%) and this severely",
                "limited the examined energy range."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The detection system consisted of four Si",
                "surface barrier detectors (Thickness: 300 to",
                "1000 mu-m; set at 10. ang. intervals) along with the",
                "corresponding electronics."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The combined errors, varying between ~11-14%",
                " (for different levels), included uncertainties in",
                "the product Q*OMEGA, in the target thickness, in",
                "peak integration, as well as, statistical",
                "uncertainties. The total experimental uncertainty",
                "was calculated following standard error propagation",
                "formulas."
              ]
            }
          ],
